  "page": "Brandon Stark (father of Walton)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For other characters with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Brandon Stark (disambiguation)\">Brandon Stark (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/50px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/75px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/100px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Brandon Stark<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Boastful</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/50px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/75px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/100px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nBrandon the Boastful</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Lord of Winterfell\">Lord of Winterfell</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_North\" title=\"Warden of the North\">Warden of the North</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/49_AC\" title=\"49 AC\">49&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Walton_Stark_(son_of_Brandon)\" title=\"Walton Stark (son of Brandon)\">Walton Stark</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Alaric_Stark\" title=\"Alaric Stark\">Alaric Stark</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Brandon Stark</b>, called <b>Brandon the Boastful</b>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> during the early reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brandon_Stark_(father_of_Walton)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Brandon succeeded <a href=\"/index.php/Roderick_Stark\" title=\"Roderick Stark\">Roderick Stark</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Lord of Winterfell\">Lord of Winterfell</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_North\" title=\"Warden of the North\">Warden of the North</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Roderick_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Roderick-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/49_AC\" title=\"49 AC\">49&#160;AC</a>, Lord Brandon attended the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Wedding\" title=\"Golden Wedding\">wedding</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> with his sons <a href=\"/index.php/Walton_Stark_(son_of_Brandon)\" title=\"Walton Stark (son of Brandon)\">Walton</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alaric_Stark\" title=\"Alaric Stark\">Alaric</a>, despite his ailing. They were accompanied by a dozen bannermen and thirty members of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>. While there, Brandon spoke with the young king <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>, profoundly praising him by claiming \"I see his <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">grandsire</a> in him.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Brandon died soon after returning to <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, the northmen believing that the strenuous journey was too much for him. Brandon was succeeded as Lord of Winterfell by his eldest son Walton.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brandon_Stark_(father_of_Walton)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Brandon Stark was the father of <a href=\"/index.php/Walton_Stark\" title=\"Walton Stark\">Walton</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alaric_Stark\" title=\"Alaric Stark\">Alaric</a>, with both of his sons successively inherited their father's titles as Lords of Winterfell.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_surfeit_of_rulers.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> His relation to his predecessor Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roderick_Stark\" title=\"Roderick Stark\">Roderick Stark</a> is unknown.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Roderick_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Roderick-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brandon<br /><small>the Boastful</small></a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black;border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;